<p><span><strong><span>微信聊天可以加超链接啦</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span>据微信派消息 </span></p>
<p><span><strong><span>从19日起</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span><strong><span>微信可以发“超链接”啦！</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201121/84961167dca84895bd9fad62cac403ba.png" /></p>
